OL,3,CManchester's development plans
OL,4,Ccriticised for inaccessibility
OL,6,F"What we'd love to do is work with
OL,7,Ftown planners, councils people
OL,8,Fbuilding work spaces and make them
OL,9,Fmore inclusive for visually impaired
OL,10,Fand disabled people more broadly,"
OL,11,Fsaid Stephen Tongue, Director of
OL,12,FFundraising at Henshaws.
OL,14,F"Often coming to town centres with
OL,15,Fpeople with low vision, or someone
OL,16,Fwith a disability ca be quite daunting
OL,17,Fbecause it's busy and there's a lot of
OL,18,Ftraffic," added Mr Steele.
