OL,3,CManchester's development plans
OL,4,Ccriticised for inaccessibility
OL,6,FManchester City Council have said
OL,7,FStevenson Square isn't finished yet
OL,8,Fand they're working with access groups
OL,9,Fto ensure everyone can safely use the
OL,10,Fspace.JTheir statement went on to say:
OL,11,F"As with any major infrastructure
OL,12,Fworks there will be a period where any
OL,13,Fidentified issues with the final
OL,14,Fdesign and finish can be rectified
OL,15,Fbefore it is fully signed off. This
OL,16,Fprocess is currently under way and the
OL,17,FCouncil is grateful for the public's
OL,18,Funderstanding during this final stage."
